00:22:41,840 --> 00:22:45,200
for breaking the law and burying her rebel brother. 

402
00:22:45,200 --> 00:22:47,960
But, of all the playwrights, Euripides is now considered 

403
00:22:47,960 --> 00:22:50,280
in many ways to have been the best. 

