00:22:50,280 --> 00:22:53,440
He wrote the play Medea, with its shocking tale 

405
00:22:53,440 --> 00:22:55,120
of a woman betrayed by her husband 

406
00:22:55,120 --> 00:22:57,800
who takes revenge by killing her own children. 

407
00:22:58,960 --> 00:23:03,600
The playwrights of ancient Athens were all gurus of the city 

