00:23:09,560 --> 00:23:13,400
and Euripides, the sort of enfant terrible of Athenian society. 

411
00:23:14,520 --> 00:23:18,720
The Greek word for playwright is "didaskalos", 

412
00:23:18,720 --> 00:23:21,000
which means "trainer", or "teacher". 

413
00:23:21,000 --> 00:23:23,680
Now, in part, that refers to the playwright's role 

414
00:23:23,680 --> 00:23:25,960
