415
00:23:25,960 --> 00:23:30,480
BUT many believe it also refers to the role of the playwright 

416
00:23:30,480 --> 00:23:35,920
in training the audience for participation in democracy itself. 

417
00:23:35,920 --> 00:23:39,600
If we take Sophocles' Ajax, as an example - 

418
00:23:39,600 --> 00:23:42,080
it's a retelling of a classic myth 

